 water path to begin the quiet search.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:55:            summary=\"Otis shares a calmer way to listen when the harbor feels too large.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:62:            summary=\"The pair follows reflected clues through glowing boats and sleepy gulls.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:69:            summary=\"The lantern reveals the hidden cove where the harbor's last promise waits.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:77:            summary=\"The tide turns and Mira fears they may miss the harbor's bedtime rhythm.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:84:            summary=\"The lantern dims for a moment and Mira thinks she has failed.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:92:            summary=\"Otis helps Mira name the fear and remember the harbor's patient rhythm.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:99:            summary=\"Mira chooses a gentler route home that uses the harbor's own lights.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:106:            summary=\"The lantern returns to its doorstep and the whole harbor settles together.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:113:            summary=\"Mira falls asleep watching the restored lights ripple over still water.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:124:            beat_sheet_summary=\"A harbor quest that lands in calm belonging.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:144:    assert \"Quest Fantasy\" in plan.summary\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:152:            beat_sheet_summary=\"A calm mystery that resolves before bed.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:173:            beat_sheet_summary=\"A harbor quest that lands in calm belonging.\",\nbackend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py:191:            beat_sheet_summary=\"A harbor quest that lands in