ess_percent)}% complete.\"\n        return \"Writing is in progress.\"\n\n    if status == RealtimeJobStatus.PAUSED:\n        if progress_percent is not None:\n            return f\"Writing paused at {round(progress_percent)}% complete.\"\n        return \"Writing is paused.\"\n\n    if status == RealtimeJobStatus.COMPLETED:\n        return _COMPOSITION_COMPLETION_MESSAGE\n\n    if status == RealtimeJobStatus.CANCELLED:\n        return job.stop_reason if job is not None and job.stop_reason else \"Writing was cancelled.\"\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '691,740p' backend/app/services/session_realtime.py\"", "exit_code": 0, "id": "item_136", "status": "completed", "type": "command_execution"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 274, "prompt_index": 66, "prompt_name": "65 \u2014 Interrupt, Pause, and Redirect Composition via Chat or UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T09:16:09-07:00"}
