{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I found the redirect-state bug: sessions are running with `autoflush=False`, so the worker was marking the request as applied in memory, then immediately querying and treating it as still pending. I\u2019m flushing that state before the cance...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_197", "text": "I found the redirect-state bug: sessions are running with `autoflush=False`, so the worker was marking the request as applied in memory, then immediately querying and treating it as still pending. I\u2019m flushing that state before the cancel path so applied redirects don\u2019t get downgraded to superseded.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 401, "prompt_index": 66, "prompt_name": "65 \u2014 Interrupt, Pause, and Redirect Composition via Chat or UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T10:56:40-07:00"}
