\"playwright\";\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:10061:    description: Use when interacting with a local webapp in this repo, taking screenshots, and verifying behavior both visually and functionally through the docker-compose dev stack and the bundled Puppeteer runner.\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:10070:    1. Start the local stack with `docker compose up -d --build`.\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:10071:    2. Confirm the app is healthy with `docker compose ps`.\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:10072:    3. Run browser checks from the `browser` service with `docker compose run --rm browser npm run check -- --spec <spec-path>`.\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:10119:    docker compose run --rm browser npm run check -- --spec ./examples/homepage.spec.json\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:12997:- Summary: in progress: /bin/zsh -lc 'cat docker-compose.yml'\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:13001:    Command: /bin/zsh -lc 'cat docker-compose.yml'\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:13009:- Summary: completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc 'cat docker-compose.yml'\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:13013:    Command: /bin/zsh -lc 'cat docker-compose.yml'\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:13199:- Summary: in progress: /bin/zsh -lc 'docker compose ps'\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:13203:    Command: /bin/zsh -lc 'docker compose ps'\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:13211:- Summary: completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc 'docker compose ps'\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:13215:    Command: /bin/zsh -lc 'docker compose ps'\n./prompts/35-chat-commands-and-quick-actions.yolopilot.md:13278:- Summary: in progress: /bin/zsh -lc 'docker compose up -d backend'\