{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The live migration uncovered another real issue: the new Alembic revision identifier is longer than the existing `alembic_version.version_num` width in Postgres, so the upgrade can\u2019t complete on an already-running stack. I\u2019m shortening t...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_305", "text": "The live migration uncovered another real issue: the new Alembic revision identifier is longer than the existing `alembic_version.version_num` width in Postgres, so the upgrade can\u2019t complete on an already-running stack. I\u2019m shortening that revision id and adding a guard test so this doesn\u2019t recur.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 594, "prompt_index": 66, "prompt_name": "65 \u2014 Interrupt, Pause, and Redirect Composition via Chat or UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T11:06:18-07:00"}
