{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The QA sessions are ready in the live app. I\u2019m capturing desktop screenshots for both queued states and a narrow/mobile shot for the redirect state so the visual verification covers the responsive control layout too.", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_329", "text": "The QA sessions are ready in the live app. I\u2019m capturing desktop screenshots for both queued states and a narrow/mobile shot for the redirect state so the visual verification covers the responsive control layout too.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 637, "prompt_index": 66, "prompt_name": "65 \u2014 Interrupt, Pause, and Redirect Composition via Chat or UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T11:09:24-07:00"}
{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0", "event_type": "Command Started", "message": "in progress: /bin/zsh -lc \"docker compose -f infra/compose/docker-compose.yml exec -T browser node --input-type=module - <<'EOF'\nimport fs from 'node:fs/promises';\nimport path from 'node:path';\nimport puppeteer from 'puppeteer';\n\nconst outputDir = '/workspace/.artifacts/webapp-qa';\nawait fs.mkdir(outputDir, { recursive: true });\n\nconst targets = [\n  {\n    name: 'prompt-65-pause-queued-desktop',\n    url: 'http://frontend:8566/sessions/95dceccd-e987-46c5-bb4d-ece34d67a4b2?stage=composition',\n    viewport: { width: 1440, height: 900 },\n    texts: [\n      'Pause queued',\n      'Pause requested. The writer will stop after the current saved chunk at about 42% complete.',\n      'Pause writing',\n    ],\n  },\n  {\n    name: 'prompt-65-redirect-queued-desktop',\n    url: 'http://frontend:8566/sessions/5381b9c3-322e-4c2a-9e3b-40475240d816?stage=composition',\n    viewport: { width: 1440, height: 900 },\n    texts: [\n      'Redirect queued',\n      'Rewrite requested from segment 2. The current chunk will finish saving before the redirect applies.',\n      'Request rewrite',\n    ],\n  },\n  {\n    name: 'prompt-65-redirect-queued-mobile',\n    url: 'http://frontend:8566/sessions/5381b9c3-322e-4c2a-9e3b-40475240d816?stage=composition',\n    viewport: { width: 420, height: 900 },\n    texts: [\n      'Redirect queued',\n      'Pending change',\n      'Rewrite guidance',\n    ],\n  },\n];\n\nconst browser = await puppeteer.launch({\n  executablePath: process.env.PUPPETEER_EXECUTABLE_PATH,\n  headless: true,\n  args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-setuid-sandbox'],\n});\n\ntry {\n  for (const target of targets) {\n    const page = await browser.newPage();\n    await page.setViewport(target.viewport);\n    await page.goto(target.url, { waitUntil: 'networkidle2', timeout: 20000 });\n    await page.waitForSelector('[data-testid=\\\"composition-main-pane\\\"]', {\n      visible: true,\n      timeout: 20000,\n    });\n    for (const text of target.texts) {\n      await page.waitForFunction(\n        (expectedText) => document.body?.innerText.includes(expectedText),\n        { timeout: 20000 },\n        text,\n      );\n    }\n    const outputPath = path.join(outputDir, \"'`${target.name}.png`);\n    await page.screenshot({ path: outputPath, fullPage: true });\n    console.log(outputPath);\n    await page.close();\n  }\n} finally {\n  await browser.close();\n}\nEOF'", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": "", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"docker compose -f infra/compose/docker-compose.yml exec -T browser node --input-type=module - <<'EOF'\nimport fs from 'node:fs/promises';\nimport path from 'node:path';\nimport puppeteer from 'puppeteer';\n\nconst outputDir = '/workspace/.artifacts/webapp-qa';\nawait fs.mkdir(outputDir, { recursive: true });\n\nconst targets = [\n  {\n    name: 'prompt-65-pause-queued-desktop',\n    url: 'http://frontend:8566/sessions/95dceccd-e987-46c5-bb4d-ece34d67a4b2?stage=composition',\n    viewport: { width: 1440, height: 900 },\n    texts: [\n      'Pause queued',\n      'Pause requested. The writer will stop after the current saved chunk at about 42% complete.',\n      'Pause writing',\n    ],\n  },\n  {\n    name: 'prompt-65-redirect-queued-desktop',\n    url: 'http://frontend:8566/sessions/5381b9c3-322e-4c2a-9e3b-40475240d816?stage=composition',\n    viewport: { width: 1440, height: 900 },\n    texts: [\n      'Redirect queued',\n      'Rewrite requested from segment 2. The current chunk will finish saving before the redirect applies.',\n      'Request rewrite',\n    ],\n  },\n  {\n    name: 'prompt-65-redirect-queued-mobile',\n    url: 'http://frontend:8566/sessions/5381b9c3-322e-4c2a-9e3b-40475240d816?stage=composition',\n    viewport: { width: 420, height: 900 },\n    texts: [\n      'Redirect queued',\n      'Pending change',\n      'Rewrite guidance',\n    ],\n  },\n];\n\nconst browser = await puppeteer.launc