{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The mobile shot now proves the disabled rewrite controls and preserved earlier manuscript, but it cuts off the `Pending change` card. I\u2019m taking one last narrow capture anchored on that card so the mobile evidence shows both the queued-s...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_339", "text": "The mobile shot now proves the disabled rewrite controls and preserved earlier manuscript, but it cuts off the `Pending change` card. I\u2019m taking one last narrow capture anchored on that card so the mobile evidence shows both the queued-state explanation and the control lockout together.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 651, "prompt_index": 66, "prompt_name": "65 \u2014 Interrupt, Pause, and Redirect Composition via Chat or UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T11:11:52-07:00"}
