{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The new intent-parser test found a real staging assumption in the fixture rather than a code regression: `_create_beats_session` never advances past beats/story setup, so forcing composition `in_progress` was invalid there. I\u2019m loosening...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_366", "text": "The new intent-parser test found a real staging assumption in the fixture rather than a code regression: `_create_beats_session` never advances past beats/story setup, so forcing composition `in_progress` was invalid there. I\u2019m loosening the fixture usage, keeping the active composition job itself, and cleaning the touched file\u2019s line-length issues at the same time.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 697, "prompt_index": 66, "prompt_name": "65 \u2014 Interrupt, Pause, and Redirect Composition via Chat or UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T11:15:31-07:00"}
