{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented prompt 65 end to end and left the code in a coherent state on the current branch. I split the work into three commits: - `f9cb89b` `feat(prompt-65): add durable composition interruptions` - `7ab27b3` `feat(prompt-65): surface...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_377", "text": "Implemented prompt 65 end to end and left the code in a coherent state on the current branch.\n\nI split the work into three commits:\n- `f9cb89b` `feat(prompt-65): add durable composition interruptions`\n- `7ab27b3` `feat(prompt-65): surface composition interruption state in the workspace`\n- `d7df006` `test(prompt-65): cover interruption-aware plan summaries`\n\nThe backend now persists interruption requests and applies them deterministically at safe composition checkpoints, with replay/hydration/realtime support. The frontend surfaces queued pause/redirect state, shows pending-change copy, and disables redundant controls while a request is pending.\n\nVerification completed:\n- `pytest backend/tests -q` -> `230 passed, 5 skipped`\n- `npm test` -> `17 files passed, 98 tests passed`\n- `npm run lint` -> passed\n- `npm run build` -> passed\n- Browser QA against the live compose stack, with screenshots at:\n  - [prompt-65-pause-queued-desktop.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-65-pause-queued-desktop.png)\n  - [prompt-65-redirect-queued-desktop.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-65-redirect-queued-desktop.png)\n  - [prompt-65-redirect-queued-mobile.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-65-redirect-queued-mobile.png)\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written as the final repository action at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/65_interrupt_pause_and_redirect_composition_via_chat_or_ui/summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"},